rationale: CC16 - lead SNP (MR analysis lung fx decline)
ME3 - lead for Tang with > 3 measurements
CHRNA5 - lead snp for COPD association, smoking behavior
IL16 - SNP Tang et al - see effect in different models
HHIP - lead variant in largest GWAS meta-analysis for lung function
AGER - lead variant for lung function, also less common
